{"tid":1232791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遊行見到差佬生擒細路","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T07:04:57.000Z","uid":211495,"like":167,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85eb2896539132beb4d9991c3f5755a29e9a0fbe","tid":1232791,"uid":211495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日行到政總附近打算排隊去廁所，點知見到兩個警察捉住個6、7歲嘅細路，個細路一直掙扎唔敢望兩個警察，原來係個細路唔見咗屋企人，警察想搵返佢屋企人，所以就捉住佢黎問佢屋企人電話之類，但個細路嘅反應真係好反感，隔離啲啊叔都話：「連細路都驚咗你地啊！」之後兩個警察即刻灰曬：「咁你地講到咁，你地處理囉！」之後就頭也不回咁byebye你條尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />BTW睇得出呢次反送中之後警察真係名譽掃地，以後小學作文「我的志願」寫做警察就同寫做乞衣差唔多咁無大志<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b549c6a4929a0800524fd12509fc93c24a787f0","tid":1232791,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"認同請分享"},{"pid":"6db46a510de9e8ab8a9ee31e5c5ad769f22052f1","tid":1232791,"uid":31749,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3faccdebddb8d3261173aea57f14dd924f9d27c","tid":1232791,"uid":228438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:00:17.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5956fdac7dde6ba6b050aaad0f44669a4e5ced26","tid":1232791,"uid":211495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:49:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3754bb8cb9b8f59d7f39148536d1d681f8d45a35","tid":1232791,"uid":249866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:51:13.000Z","msg":"好波 抵撚死"},{"pid":"f8c7f0afcdbaef4d1ad89e327bbe134b9076659a","tid":1232791,"uid":35747,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"痴線，咁絕對唔係好事。<br />\n係咁岩係隔離遊行既人係好人姐，如果個人心懷不軌咁點算，所以警察係一定要理佢，要幫佢。<br />\n<br />\n唔好反到傻左啦。無晒警察，同無晒外傭一樣，係對香港有好大衝擊架。"},{"pid":"2ecc56